, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 14:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863222937,45974302,3306]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63849256]·发发发[/uid] (2026-04-02 14:11):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，国算可以补点吗[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>这种时候能补做T的 一定是那个板块的大哥肯定是红的才行  不然都没有对标", "lou": 1730, "content_length": 70, "reply_to": 863222937, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775110423}, {"pid": 863223623, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 14:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863223504,45974302,3306]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39615300]名声丶在外[/uid] (2026-04-02 14:15):[/b]<br/><br/>全都在躲清明劫，逆回购狂跌[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>没事 抄底资金进来了", "lou": 1731, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 863223504, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775110608}, {"pid": 863223926, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 14:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "刚才出金的 和恐慌的  明天不懂用什么姿势追回来", "lou": 1732, "content_length": 42, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775110740}, {"pid": 863224362, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 14:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863224197,45974302,3307]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42162697]baozimusic[/uid] (2026-04-02 14:20):[/b]<br/><br/>所以狼大明天还是看到3955附近能到一次吗[s:ac:晕]我还以为博弈清明+复活节正反手封盘的人很多，明天冲不了高来着[/quote]<br/>明天不一定  但是会往这个方向。如果明天冲3955 这些机构一卖  那被套住的散户要经历  恐怖难熬的三天。。。。", "lou": 1733, "content_length": 101, "reply_to": 863224197, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775110927}, {"pid": 863224471, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 14:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863224262,4597430